行裡面這種人很多，至少我在這裡堵住了一個。<br />\n<br />\n也在此警告所有加入我的人：非誠勿擾。我在訓練的是最強的團隊，你基礎不好不要緊，但你態度不好，我就給你一個人生教訓。<br />\n<br />\n這只是我的第一步。即使你爸爸媽媽來找我都會繼續。我希望你身邊所有的人都恥笑你。<br />\n<br />\n回港大校園，我要走過你的人談論你。<br />\n<br />\nWhat a loser.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S98d2oD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS98d2oD.png&h=4386c060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:24:53.000Z","msg":"公審連個中文全名都無公你條毛咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:25:23.000Z","msg":"有圖都認到啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:29:21.000Z","msg":"ON9<br />\n換個髮型張相仲認閪到<br />\n又要公審人又要審得咁撚驚死正pussy 懦夫, <br />\n垃圾林作。"},{"pid":"3b427c6e9855893510b7146bc8e77b209415710c","tid":2517161,"uid":60219,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:29:26.000Z","msg":"無交代都唔緊要<br />\n退出都唔緊要<br />\n話保險狗都唔緊要<br />\n但係彈出彈入喎大佬，想唔嬲都難啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f73dd5e88a2507921ee62aa6a189ac30df1f6aa","tid":2517161,"uid":68884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:29:55.000Z","msg":"作仔啲中文差到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點樣「公開呼籲此人是垃圾」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5629f91caa2c1e54c918137bd35b625e320df23","tid":2517161,"uid":378185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"冇交帶真係抵撚死"},{"pid":"b00fd210d90c16c745e8bb38e8787c76d91aa457","tid":2517161,"uid":218494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:32:23.000Z","msg":"作仔條撚樣真係最好打巢鐘培生，如果唔係真係想睇下邊個俾人笑成世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=